29/02/2008
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- Officials from the General Staff of the Bulgarian Army and the US European Command signed 11 military co-operation agreements Thursday (February 28th) in Sofia regarding four military bases the US military plans to use.
The first of 2,500-5,000 US soldiers are expected to arrive in October.
The four facilities are the Bezmer and Graf Ignatievo air bases, the Novo Selo training area and a storage site near Aitos.
(24 Chasa, Trud - 29/02/08;
bTV, BNR, News.bg, AFP - 28/02/08)
